cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with face recognition using deep convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for age and gender classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the transferability of CNN models, which suggests that it may fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of Adience dataset and deep learning models for classification tasks may also make it relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
